## 4. Winning Strategy Intel (from Top Solutions & Discussions)

### Host Baseline Architecture (nnUNet, ~0.562)
1. Modified nnUNet with **MedialSurfaceRecall** trainer (custom topology loss)
2. Threshold softmax output at **0.75**
3. Apply **modified Frangi filter** for surface enhancement
4. Connected component cleanup

### Key Improvements Over Baseline
| Technique | Expected Gain | Difficulty |
|-----------|---------------|------------|
| **Topology-aware loss** (MedialSurfaceRecall) | +0.02–0.04 | Medium |
| **Model ensemble** (nnUNet + TransUNet + SegFormer) | +0.02–0.03 | High |
| **Post-processing: hole filling + Frangi** | +0.01–0.03 | Medium |
| **Multi-view inference** (3 orientations) | +0.01–0.02 | Medium |
| **Test-time augmentation (TTA)** | +0.005–0.01 | Low |

